replies.body:
you can... in ranked 5's when the synergy between your picks can be perfectly utilized through voice comms and planning.

Have you not seen the "Protect the Yi" Comps.

Top: {{champion:117}}
Jungle: {{champion:11}} 
Mid: {{champion:26}} OR {{champion:61}} 
Bot: {{champion:43}} {{champion:40}} OR {{champion:25}} 

Comps like this are fun and can work, but require some sort of coordination and trust in the Yi player to carry.

There are a lot of "Support the X" team comps where people play 4 supports and 1 hyper carry champion that builds full damage and relies on his team to keep him alive.

The most common is the "Jugger'maw", where you play support style champion to keep your ADC {{champion:96}} alive.
